arts.ttl: Karim Benzema vs Cristiano Ronaldo: Real Madrid Legends Face Off as Al Ittihad Take on Al Nassr
arts.sum: Many notable names will be in action for the high-stakes match, including two Real Madrid legends in Karim Benzema and Cristiano Ronaldo. One, if not both, of the teams will lose their 100% record in the Saudi Pro League, as both sides have won all three of their games so far this season.
